result.title: CodeMania — Android App for Programmers
result.content:
Hello Community , I am happy to announce Play Store release of CodeMania — App to keep you up to date with programming world. The app is in development phase and seeks further improvement . Rate and Review , Check out ratings of your competitors at one go. Keep yourself updated with upcoming contests. It is open sourced on Github .
Feel free to contribute !! Contributors — prasoonbatham capta1n
